resources.string: Truiton\'s device admin implementation which shows the usage of DevicePolicyManager class. This implementation provides you a way to control a device\'s security.
Truiton Device Admin helps the user to get special privileges, for eg. to access the Truiton network data. These privileges can only be acquired by accepting these policies.
